.TH "create_of_modalias" 9 "create_of_modalias" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
create_of_modalias \- Creates DT compatible string for modalias and uevent
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" create_of_modalias
.BI "(struct acpi_device *acpi_dev "  ","
.BI "char *modalias "  ","
.BI "int size "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "acpi_dev" 12
ACPI device object.
.IP "modalias" 12
Buffer to print into.
.IP "size" 12
Size of the buffer.
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Expose DT compatible modalias as of:NnameTCcompatible.  This function should
only be called for devices having ACPI_DT_NAMESPACE_HID in their list of
ACPI/PNP IDs.
